name: Personalised custom bracelet
description:
These customised bracelets are made of high quality black plastic beads, white alphabet beads and strong elastic. They are perfect for gifts or for yourself, look great on anyone, and are one size fits all so will fit most adults and teenagers. Choose a name, quote, favourite band or musician, fandom name, special events or anything you want!

Choose any word(s) containing up to 20 letters or numbers.

Please add a message to buyer during payment with the word(s) you would like on the bracelet. Please allow a couple of days for the items to be dispatched as the bracelets are handmade. I will always try to ship all items within 2 working days of purchase. I try my best to keep my prices competitive and at the lowest price I can!
